result.name: Mrs. Pound

reviews.text: Love everything about this place! The awesome decor, music and food. So far nothing has disappointed. It's Asian fusion.
I love hidden speakeasy bars! This one is pretending to be a locksmith just off Hollywood Rood bear Cat Street. Drinks were delicious and staff was super friendly. Food was good, not great.
Nice little bar restaurant in the heart of Sheung Wan with very nice cocktails and food for lunch.
Interesting concept. While food was good, it was quite pricy.
Did I walk right by it at first? Maybe. But I found the hidden entrance eventually, and that’s all that counts. Drinks were nice, and the meatballs with the raw egg, too.
